title: AutoMapa 5.0.5 + Europe Maps
description:
AutoMapa 5 - It will take you where you want. Right on target.

Nearly 700 cities and locations with buildings in a 3D view. The revolutionary user interface makes navigation child&#039;s play. New, even more detailed maps and more than 220 000 Points of Interest (POI) enable the user to find nearly every petrol station, ATM or club. Once again, AutoMapa 5 sets new navigation standards!

Pack:
- AutoMapa 5.0.5
- Maps of:
Austria
Belgium
Croatia
Czech Republic
Denmark
Estonia
Finnland
France
Spain 
the Netherlands
Ireland
Lithuania
Latvia
Luxembourg
Germany
Norway
Poland
Portugal
Slovakia
Slovenia
Switzerland
Sweden
Hungary
Great Britain
Italy

Additionally, main roads joining Albania, Bosnia, Moldavia, Romania, The Republic of Serbia.

Installation:
1. Mount automapa_505.iso in DAEMON Tools or burn on DVD.
2. Install with instruction http://www.xeonv.com/photogallery.php?album_id=11
Attention at "Krok 8" you need to unselect "Rejestruj" (eng "Register")!!!
3. Done :)

Works in 100%, tested on PDA: Mio P550

By Xeon :)
